result.name: Chee Kei

reviews.text: Got the wonton noodle combo with drink and dessert. Everything was tasting good until I discovered a giant bug in my noodles!!!! So disgusting they offered to give me another bowl but I lost my appetite..

This is a comfortable restaurant situated in a very nice shopping centre. We ordered wanton noodle and beef brisket with wanton noodles. The wantons are delicious and big. U can taste the prawn in each wanton. Their fishballs is also delicious but could be a bit big for a mouthful, it’s about 3cm in diameter. We saw many customers ordering their barley drink, big cup with plenty of barley. The price is reasonable for Hongkong standard.
I ordered noodle soup. Tasted OK. But lacks in presentation.  Smaller than expected serving size.

Good hongkong wantons and noodles. Set meal are easy for ordering and offer different options to try hongkong famous noodle/wantons. Reasonably priced , given that it's in touristy area. Food service is fast. Beef brisket is really good too, so soft and rich in flavor. Recommend this
One of the remaining HK eatery with previous local standard but can be costly

result.name: 池記

reviews.text: 特別喜爱薏米茶🍵想喝時我必首選这裹，還有店家使用余均益辣椒醬也是我至愛👍😘
雖然裝修咗舒服咗啲，不過食物冇以前咁好味，價錢又貴咗

$77包括了麵食，小吃和飲品一杯。好味的雲吞麵和炸鯪魚球，是傳統的廣東小吃，現在已買少見少。份量不多，是輕食的好選擇。

光顧日期：19 June 2019
一間港式特色粥、粉、麵、飯和甜品的食店，主要菜式包括薏米水，桑寄生蛋茶，炸鯪魚球，雲吞麵，紅油三寶，牛筋麵等，雖然食物分量不算很大份，味道尚可，但價錢略貴。
快餐式粥麵店，不特別好吃
